      <hedline>
        <hl1>LOSSES GROW AT STORAGENETWORKS</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>StorageNetworks Inc reports second-quarter net loss of $31.3 million, compared with $3 million a year ago; shares fall $7.625, to $130 (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Shares of cobiStorageNetworks Inc. fell after it reported that despite a sharp jump in revenue its net losses increased tenfold in the second quarter from a year earlier. The data storage company based in Waltham, Mass., reported a second-quarter net loss of $31.3 million, compared with $3 million a year earlier. The shares fell $7.625, to $130.</p>
        <p>NYTimes.com/TheStreet.com</p>
      </block>
